Please don't forget the So What Test

2
00:00:02,424 --> 00:00:04,826
when you're presenting.

3
00:00:04,826 --> 00:00:08,420
Is this slide or this topic relevant or not?

4
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,670
Is the music in this slide,

5
00:00:11,814 --> 00:00:14,823
if you're gonna use it, right, relevant?

6
00:00:14,823 --> 00:00:16,935
Is the quote relevant?

7
00:00:16,935 --> 00:00:19,556
Is the image relevant?

8
00:00:19,556 --> 00:00:22,439
So it's crucial that you please remember

9
00:00:22,439 --> 00:00:25,818
the characteristics and background of your audience

10
00:00:25,818 --> 00:00:28,058
in order to make sure that your speech

11
00:00:28,058 --> 00:00:29,978
is relevant to them.

12
00:00:29,978 --> 00:00:31,706
And if you aren't sure if it is,

13
00:00:31,706 --> 00:00:34,249
