14
00:00:34,249 --> 00:00:36,186
called Who is the Audience

15
00:00:36,186 --> 00:00:39,450
or Customers Plus Their Characteristics.

16
00:00:39,450 --> 00:00:43,529
Also, please review Journal Exercise Number Three

17
00:00:43,529 --> 00:00:46,821
on What is the Number One Goal or Purpose

18
00:00:46,821 --> 00:00:48,474
of Your Presentation?

19
00:00:48,474 --> 00:00:50,377
We do that just to make sure

20
